# feishu-codex-bridge (Go) CODEOWNERS
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Order matters: the LAST matching pattern for a file wins. Keep generic
# patterns at the top and progressively narrow down by directory below.
#
# Owners listed here are auto-requested as reviewers when a PR touches the
# matching paths. Combined with branch-protection ("Require review from Code
# Owners"), every change to a sensitive surface is signed off by its maintainer
# — including changes authored by AI agents.
#
# 当前仓库单一维护者；分区结构为未来新增 reviewer 预留（在对应区域加 handle 即可）。
# area 划分见 AGENTS.md「目录入口速查」与 .github/labels.yml 的 area: 组。

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default fallback — every file not matched by a more specific rule below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                   @pxguan

